    <item>
      <title>韩国医生寻求避免与律师相同的命运</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/south-korean-doctors-seek-to-avoid-same-fate-as-lawyers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国领导人推动迅速结束医生罢工以抗议增加医科学生人数的计划，这可能会因法学院采取的类似举措而蒙上阴影，导致律师人数增加，平均工资下降 20% 以上。十年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/south-korean-doctors-seek-to-avoid-same-fate-as-lawyers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 09:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
